    "body": "Why don't we have something like : \n\n``` javascript\nvar instantsearch = require('instantsearch').make;\nvar search = instantsearch(appId, apiKey, indexName);\n```\n\nI'm not sure about the key used here (make) but I think that's easy to instanciate and use. Don't you think?\n",
