    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Honestly I would be a bit surprised by this kind of API.\n\nDocumentation tooling aside, given our previous modules, I would advocate for something like:\n\n``` js\nvar instantsearch = require('instantsearch');\nvar search = instantsearch(appId, apiKey, indexName);\n```\n\nI know @bobylito this is not what you prefer, adding it because I feel this is straightforward.\n",
